{"tid":379199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【社會實驗】小學生700蚊散紙放巴士站任攞","createTime":"2017-08-29T06:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T08:04:15.000Z","uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5cfee278301d732e0376c6da323957d00f1ce2","tid":379199,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170829&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57138637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170829%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57138637&d=NCCDkho3GobewTXrfFF8TZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=543bd739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170829%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57138637&h=ee9eac89\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170829&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57138637</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1fiz4bo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1fiz4bo&h=3a6cf31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9lig3ntw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9lig3ntw&h=173b0203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n匆忙趕到巴士站先發現身上無散紙，有兜硬幣就在旁邊，你會拿來用嗎？會否一天就被拿光？河北邯鄲市邯山區實驗小學的三年級學生紀雨杭，就把自己700元（人民幣‧下同）零用錢換成硬幣，裝到紙箱中放在人流比較多的巴士站，為坐巴士而沒有零錢的市民朋友提供方便。他先後進行了5天，分別選擇了5個巴士站，目前剩餘還<br />\n有450元左右。"},{"pid":"0f4fdea2d1dca2543bbb9c29f3dbff65ca752887","tid":379199,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"有多散紙唔通會放返落去咩"},{"pid":"7fa37caccae9ad207d18702b99eb0bf5be7fa117","tid":379199,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"呢個世界，有好嘅壞仔，同唔好嘅壞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ff22c033c48d5035844612c865f417e2cfab42","tid":379199,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"幾有趣"},{"pid":"7ba50908cfaa6fc9ce79d8973f64d07171080193","tid":379199,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"竟然冇比支那人攞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88f3c95f2c68960dbf6e230458f6e00ef860d8d","tid":379199,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"每到一處，紀雨杭和自己爸爸、媽媽，就把零錢箱和牌子放到巴士站牌子的旁邊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>悄悄地站在遠處觀看</strong></span>。期間目擊人生百態：有人一把就抓了好幾十個硬幣就走。第二次，又見那個人來拿錢，他們沒理會，紀雨杭說：「這哪裡是坐公交車呀，都夠他的中午飯錢了。」到第三次看到的時候，紀雨杭着急了，他拉着我就喊：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">媽，快去（阻止）！</span></strong>」幸好，放置零錢箱的5天時間，市民還挺守規矩，目前還剩下450元多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任攞??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd5704f6ff6ec5e47f1f7190288827e19afd44f","tid":379199,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"人地有寫明每人攞2蚊"},{"pid":"f5529651ba79e92a44d4a1017b18ad2e401c7be7","tid":379199,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有寫明每人攞2蚊</blockquote><br />\n中英聯合聲明夠寫明五十年內不變"},{"pid":"2b69cb0dae554b7dba13f5c9c5695df254cd9b31","tid":379199,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地有寫明每人攞2蚊</blockquote><br />\n中英聯合聲明夠寫明五十年內不變</blockquote><br />\n咁都拉到去第樣 算啦"},{"pid":"02609c578e7aa6ec210a102ba836143af42062b9","tid":379199,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地有寫明每人攞2蚊</blockquote><br />\n中英聯合聲明夠寫明五十年內不變</blockquote><br />\n咁都拉到去第樣 算啦</blockquote><br />\n都係講緊信用<br />\n有乜分別"},{"pid":"213c401e0c4da04bfa06e78d5fd99f32f8d6afb3","tid":379199,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><b